To activate Expert Mode in Terraria, follow these steps:

1. Start a new world or select an existing world.
2. In the world creation menu, locate the Difficulty option.
3. Change the Difficulty setting to "Expert".
4. Customize any other world settings you desire.
5. Create the world and enter into it.

Once you're in Expert Mode, be prepared for a more challenging and rewarding Terraria experience. Enemies will be stronger, bosses will have new abilities, and there will be additional items and boss drops to acquire. Good luck!
